                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Sezione per le Migrazioni</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/giubileo-e-migrazioni-camminare-insieme-nella-speranza/" rel="bookmark">«Giubileo e Migrazioni: Camminare insieme nella speranza»</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Incontro della Sezione per le Migrazioni della Commissione per la Pastorale Sociale del CCEE</h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/giubileo-e-migrazioni-camminare-insieme-nella-speranza/" title="«Giubileo e Migrazioni: Camminare insieme nella speranza»"><img width="800" height="490" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-800x490.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-800x490.png 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-380x233.png 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-1024x627.png 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-768x470.png 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-600x367.png 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-1200x735.png 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1-1320x808.png 1320w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-12-12-v-14.33.21-1.png 1382w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></a>                                                </header><!-- .entry-header -->
