                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Dialogo Interreligioso</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/nostra-aetate-60-anni-dopo-prospettive-sul-dialogo-tra-cattolici-e-musulmani/" rel="bookmark">«Nostra Aetate, 60 anni dopo: Prospettive sul dialogo tra cattolici e musulmani»</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Incontro della Sezione per il Dialogo Interreligioso della Commissione per l’Evangelizzazione e la Cultura del CCEE</h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/nostra-aetate-60-anni-dopo-prospettive-sul-dialogo-tra-cattolici-e-musulmani/" title="«Nostra Aetate, 60 anni dopo: Prospettive sul dialogo tra cattolici e musulmani»"><img width="800" height="534" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-800x534.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_4457204333074480702_n-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/12/589736375_831613689843429_44572043330744