                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Consulenti giuridici</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/revisione-del-diritto-canonico-e-riforma-della-chiesa/" rel="bookmark">«Revisione del Diritto canonico e riforma della Chiesa»</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Incontro dei consulenti giuridici a Edimburgo</h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/revisione-del-diritto-canonico-e-riforma-della-chiesa/" title="«Revisione del Diritto canonico e riforma della Chiesa»"><img width="800" height="358" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-800x358.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-800x358.jpg 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-380x170.jpg 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-1024x459.jpg 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-768x344.jpg 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-1536x688.jpg 1536w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-2048x918.jpg 2048w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-600x269.jpg 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-1200x538.jpg 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/07abe6e9-1320-4214-80bc-83221b22139e-1320x591.jpg 1320w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></a>                                                </header><!-- .entry-header -->
