                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Ecumenismo</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/la-charta-oecumenica-aggiornata-rappresenta-una-pietra-miliare-verso-lunita-dei-cristiani-in-europa/" rel="bookmark">La Charta Œcumenica aggiornata rappresenta una pietra miliare verso l’unità dei Cristiani in Europa</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Una versione riveduta firmata ufficialmente a Roma dai Presidenti del CCEE e del CEC.</h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/la-charta-oecumenica-aggiornata-rappresenta-una-pietra-miliare-verso-lunita-dei-cristiani-in-europa/" title="La Charta Œcumenica aggiornata rappresenta una pietra miliare verso l’unità dei Cristiani in Europa"><img width="800" height="533" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-800x533.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-272x182.jpg 272w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/11/DSC_5082-1320x880.jpg 1320w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></a>                                                </header><!-- .entry-header -->
