                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Comitato congiunto CCEE-CEC</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/il-comitato-congiunto-ccee-cec-e-la-firma-della-charta-oecumenica-aggiornata/" rel="bookmark">Il Comitato Congiunto CCEE–CEC e la firma della Charta Œcumenica aggiornata</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Papa Leone XIV riceve in udienza i partecipanti alla cerimonia della firma</h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/il-comitato-congiunto-ccee-cec-e-la-firma-della-charta-oecumenica-aggiornata/" title="Il Comitato Congiunto CCEE–CEC e la firma della Charta Œcumenica aggiornata"><img width="800" height="677" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-800x677.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-800x677.png 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-380x322.png 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-1024x867.png 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-768x650.png 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-600x508.png 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-1200x1016.png 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39-1320x1117.png 1320w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Snimek-obrazovky-2025-10-21-v-14.12.39.png 1380w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></a>                                                </header><!-- .entry-header --