                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Sezione Cultura</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/leuropa-e-la-cultura-cristiana/" rel="bookmark">«L’Europa e la cultura Cristiana»</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Incontro dei vescovi e dei direttori nazionali</h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/leuropa-e-la-cultura-cristiana/" title="«L’Europa e la cultura Cristiana»"><img width="800" height="533" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-800x533.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-272x182.jpg 272w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/10/Torino_-_Duomo_di_Torino_-_2023-09-14_11-45-03_001-1320x880.jpg 1320w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></a>                                                </header><!-- .entry-header -->
