                    <h4 class="seed_wp_starter_so_occhiello">Assemblea plenaria/3</h4>            <h2 class="entry-title-post" itemprop="headline"><a href="https://www.ccee.eu/cardinale-grech-e-il-ruolo-del-vescovo-in-una-chiesa-sinodale/" rel="bookmark">Cardinale Grech e il ruolo del vescovo in una Chiesa sinodale</a></h2>                <h2 class="seed_wp_starter_so_sottotitolo">Una relazione nella seconda sessione dei lavori </h2>                                                <a href="https://www.ccee.eu/cardinale-grech-e-il-ruolo-del-vescovo-in-una-chiesa-sinodale/" title="Cardinale Grech e il ruolo del vescovo in una Chiesa sinodale"><img width="800" height="534" src="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-800x534.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-800x534.jpg 800w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-380x253.jpg 380w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-272x182.jpg 272w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007-1320x880.jpg 1320w, https://www.ccee.eu/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2023/11/IMG-20231128-WA0007.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"></a>                                                </header><!-- .entry-header -->
